casebody.data:
Michael S. GORBEY, petitioner,
v.
William TAYLOR, Warden, et al. No. 16-7052. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 9, 2017.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit denied.

The CHIEF JUSTICE and Justice KAGAN took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
